			<div class="terms">
				<p class="title">Terms and Conditions</p>
				<p><b>Stamped.</b> is a business card design and print service that caters to bulk orders and individual orders.</p>
				<p>1. It is the client full responsibility to read and understand the terms and condition stated below. Ordering from the online store means that you have read and understand the terms and conditions listed below.</p>
				<p>2. All orders must be paid in full before printing the approved invites.</p>
				<p>3. Only 5 drafts are allowed. In excess additional P150 payment per revision. One email revision even if it is a one letter change is equivalent to 1 draft. Please check spelling/s first before sending the file to avoid charges.</p>
				<p>4. Please proof your design and wording during the design process. Once you give the final written approval for your design, STAMPED. is not responsible for errors including typographical or formatting on the final product. All errors, including spelling, punctuation, layout, format and typestyle, are the full responsibility of the client. No exceptions.</p>
				<p>5. With respect to our fellow artist and supplier with their designs, we will only take inspirations from the given peg the client presented. We only layout with our existing designs on hand and can make minor revisions to complement your design peg. Copyright is punishable under the law.</p>
				<p>6. All revisions after the confirmed approval is subject for a pull-out fee of Php500 granted we havenâ€™t started printing it yet.</p>
				<p>7. Only payment in cash is accepted (bank transfers are also permitted). The person who signs the contract form is responsible for the full payment. Deposit fees are non refundable and not consumable once client choose not to proceed with the contract package.</p>
				<p>8. Shipping fee is not included.</p>
				<p>9. Cut off on submitting orders to production is every Friday. Printing takes 15 working days after the Friday cutoff (SAT and SUN not included) Printing starts upon approval of final artwork. Special treatments, such as Foil or Emboss, please add 3 working days.</p>
				<p>10. Request for high resolution files is P2000.</p>
				<p>11. Client supplied files must be in high resolution with a minimum of 300dpi. Please ask us for sizing and cutting guide templates.</p>
				<p>12. Digital soft copy for proofing may vary from different computer screens. Check the pantone colors for accurate comparison. </p>
				<p>13. Reprint of invitation is 10 working days. (SAT and SUN not included).</p>
				<p>14. We use a variety of paper types. We will not accept verbal paper request, only thru email after we have sent the final pdf file for the final approval. </p>
				<p>15. We try our best to proof read your details but due to the personalized nature of this service, NO REFUND / RE PRINTING will be issued once printing has started. Therefore be extra careful when giving us the OK for the artwork.</p>
				<p>16. Non transferrable </p>
